          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780553119152" href="/book/show/878166.The_Mysterious_Affair_at_Styles">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
